"{\"uid\": \"newzimbabwe.com-sensational-paris-olympics-come-to-an-end\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Date:  By BBC Sport  STARS of sport, screen and music came together at the Paris 2024 closing ceremony to bring the 33rd Olympic Games to an end.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 145, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 10, \"end\": 19, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Online\", \"score\": 0.9934732283656572, \"rank\": 0.005859237264610976, \"text\": \"BBC Sport\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Online\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Online\"}, {\"begin\": 75, \"end\": 85, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.4512950956881166e-22, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Actor Tom Cruise descended from the roof of Stade de France to collect the Olympic flag as part of the handover to the American city of Los Angeles, which will host the next Games in 2028, before departing on a motorcycle.Red Hot Chili Peppers, Billie Eilish, Snoop Dogg and Dr Dre then performed on Venice Beach as part of a star-studded music set to conclude the ceremony.Earlier, inside the stadium in Paris, gold medallists Alex Yee and Bryony Page were Great Britain's flagbearers at the ceremony.Actor Tom Cruise descended from the roof of the stadium to collect the Olympic flag, before departing on a motorcycle to begin its journey across the AtlanticYee won the men's triathlon in dramatic fashion, while Page won Britain's first ever Olympic trampoline gold.Great Britain finished seventh in the medal table with 14 gold, 22 silver and 29 bronze.\", \"from\": 147, \"to\": 1004, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 153, \"end\": 163, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Cruise\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tom Cruise